Asīmakṛṣṇa — the son of Aśvamedhaja, and the father <BR>of Nemicakra;1 was king when the Vāyu Purāṇa was <BR>uttered.2 1) Bhā. IX. 22. 39.<BR> 2) Vā. 1. 12.<BR>

