Āśrāyaṇis — a group of sages of Kaśyapa gotra. <BR>M. 199. 2.

आश्लेषा
Āśleṣā — on the left hind foot of the Śiśumāra.1 Its im<BR>portance for śrāddha;2 the seventh nakṣatra.3 1) Bhā. V. 23. 6; Br. II. 24. 135.<BR> 2) Br. III. 18. 5.<BR> 3) Vā. 82. 5.<BR>

