Iḍāvatsara — the third year of a five year yuga. Also <BR>Idvatsara;1 is Soma or moon.2 1) Bhā. III. 11. 14; V. 22. 7; Vi. II. 8. 72; 13. 115; Vā. 50. 183.<BR> 2) Br. II. 13. 118; 129; 21. 132; 28. 22. M. 141. 18. Vā. 31. 30; 56. 20.<BR>

