Indu (I) — a name of Soma (s.v.). <BR>Br. II. 19. 134; 37. 44; III. 65. 21; Vā. 63. 41; Vi. I. 15. 77.

इन्दु
Indu (II) — the son of Viśvaga. <BR>M. 12. 29.

इन्दु
Indu (III) — Moon — married the 27 Mānasa daughters <BR>of Dakṣa. <BR>Vā. 63. 41.

