Kunti (II) — the son of Kratha and father of Dhṛṣṭi(a) <BR>(Vṛṣṇi-Burnouf). <BR>Bhā. IX. 24. 3; M. 44. 38-9; Vā. 95. 38; Vi. IV. 12. 40-41.

