decease of Rāma, Kṛṣṇa and <BR>others; entered fire.10 1) Bhā. I. 1. 12; III. 1. 33; 2. 25; IX. 24. 23, 45, 53; X. 1. 8 <BR>and 29; 36. 17; Br. I. 1. 125; M. 44. 73; 46. 13-15; 47. 2; Vā. 1. <BR>148; 96. 163, 172-4; Vi. IV. 14. 18; 15. 18. 26-30.<BR> 2) Bhā. X. Chh. <BR>1-4; 44. 50-51; 45. 1-12; Bhā. I. 8. 23. 33; 11. 28; X. 36. 20; 43. 24. <BR>Vi. V. 2. 2; 4. 14; 18. 7-8.<BR> 3) Bhā. I. 14. 27.<BR> 4) Ib. X. [67 (V) 48].<BR> 5) Ib. X. 55. 35.<BR> 6) Ib. X. 56. 34-5.<BR> 7) Ib. XI. 5. 51.<BR> 8) Ib. X. 82. 37.<BR> 9) Ib. X. 85. 27-33, 52, 56-70.<BR> 10) Ib. XI. 31. 18; Vi. V. 38. 4.<BR>

