Mandara (VII) — a Mt. in Malayadvīpa. <BR>Vā. 48. 23.

मन्दर
Mandara (VIII) — a hill on the east of Ilāvṛta. <BR>Vi. II. 2. 18.

मन्दरशोभि
Mandaraśobhi — a son of Maṇibhadra. <BR>Vā. 69. 155.

मन्दरहरिण
Mandarahariṇa — an upadvīpa to Jambūdvīpa. <BR>Bhā. V. 19. 30.

मन्दराचल
Mandarācala — a chief hill of Kuśadvīpa. <BR>Vi. II. 4. 41.

मन्दवाहिनी
Mandavāhinī — R. from Śuktimanta (Śuktimat). <BR>M. 114. 32; Vā. 45. 107.

मन्दवाह्य
Mandavāhya — a son of Sāraṇa. <BR>Vā. 96. 165.

