by all; a good king; his rule and <BR>achievements, including the milking of the earth by all <BR>beings.6 1) Bhā. IV. 13. 18-20; 35. 38; Br. II. 35. 122; M. 4. 44.<BR> 2) Bhā. <BR>IV. 13. 39, 42 and 47; ch. 14 (whole).<BR> 3) Ib. IV. 15. 1-3; 16. 11; <BR>X. 73. 20.<BR> 4) Ib. II. 7. 9; VII. 1. 16; Br. II. 36. 108-12, 121-27, 150.<BR> 5) M. 10. 4-10.<BR> 6) Vā. 62. 108-193.<BR>

