शिष्ट
Śiṣṭas — also designated Śanta and sādhus; those who <BR>have conquered the senses; sādhu brahmacāri, sādhu <BR>gṛhasta, sādhu vaikhānasa and sādhu yati by yoga practice; <BR>followers of smārta and śrauta karmas; put in practice ācāra <BR>which is eightfold; jitātmans. <BR>Br. II. 32. 19-53; 35. 192.

शिष्टाचार
