Śiṣṭi — a son of Dhruva; wife Succhāyā; Ripu and four <BR>other sons. <BR>Vi. I. 13. 1.

शिसुक
Śisuka — a grandson of Nandiyaśa, ruled in Purīkā. <BR>Vā. 99. 370.

शीक्षा
Śīkṣā — a part of Viṣṇu. <BR>Vi. V. 1. 37.

