Śukra (IV) — the Nāga presiding over the month of <BR>Śuci. <BR>Bhā. XII. 11. 36.

शुक्र
Śukra (V) — a son of Ūru and Āgneyī. <BR>Br. II. 36. 108.

शुक्र
Śukra (VI) — a name of Śiva. <BR>Br. III. 72. 183.

शुक्र
Śukra (VII) — one of the twenty Sutapa gaṇas. <BR>Br. IV. 1. 14; Vā. 100. 14.

