Śukra (VIII) — a son of Ūrjā and Vasiṣṭha: a sage of the <BR>epoch of Bhautya Manu; of the XIV epoch of Manu. <BR>Br. IV. 1. 113; Vi. I. 10. 13; III. 2. 44.

