Śukra (XII) — a son of Prajāpati and overlord of Daityas;1 <BR>mother of, brought back to life by Bhṛgu.2 1) Vā. 10. 72; 38. 62; 53. 33.<BR> 2) Ib. 1. 150.<BR>

